Text: ugh i feel this..i miss being too busy to eat

Author: sickcupcake
Text: Me, too! My first summer class is over and now I’m waiting until mid July for my second one to start so I can keep busy until fall semester. I hate summer. I miss my school routine and wish I would’ve started a job as soon as the semester ended. I’ve gained 5-10 pounds, depending on how heavily I restrict during the week. The munchies hit HARD and my boyfriend loves to take us to get late night Taco Bell and snacks. I absolutely have to lose these 5-10 pounds, plus more, because I really want to start my senior year skinny. I WILL start my senior year skinny. Have to.
